column11: We are accessing the register bank 0, which in this case are adressed 0x00 to 0x7F
We are now looking at adress 0x00 in register bank 0, which is the WHO_AM_I. We are supposed to obtain 0xEA, which we do.
Accessing once again the register bank 0
We are now setting up the power management of the module. We check to see if the values present are correct. If they are not, we change them to 0x81, which is the case.
